    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start for the atmosphere. now i want to zoom in a bit more on the people. i want to show the tension through the characters the protagonist sees while walking through. can you describe some of the people hanging out on the street corners or in the doorways? i want them to feel like part of the \"danger\" or the \"social decay\" i mentioned—give me some specific details about what they look like or how they're acting to really drive that point home.",
