      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Shoulders are hunched against an unseen chill, even in the summer heat, as groups congregate near overflowing dumpsters. Their clothing is a patchwork of faded athletic wear and cheap, ill-fitting leather, often layered with visible signs of struggle. Eyes dart constantly, a nervous, territorial vigilance that suggests everyone is either waiting for something or actively avoiding something. They communicate in clipped murmurs and aggressive gestures, creating an impenetrable, watchful perimeter along the walkways.",
      "source": "target",
